@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Completed
Completed --> Created : reject
Created --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Reviewed : confirm
Archived : entry / log department
Reviewed --> Closed : approve
Closed --> Processing : update
Completed --> Processing : revert
Processing --> [*]
@enduml